<title>USA: Think New Ideas completes acquisition.</title>
<headline>Think New Ideas completes acquisition.</headline>
<dateline>NEW YORK 1997-06-19</dateline>
<text>
<p>Think New Ideas Inc said on Thursday that it completed its acquisition of the assets of Fathom Advertising from Omnicom Group Inc for stock.</p>
<p>The transaction, valued at about $500,000, increases Omnicom's stake in Think New Ideas to about 19 percent from 16.6 percent.</p>
<p>Fathom is the agency for Oracle Corp, and the account will be handled by the expanded Think New Ideas operation, the company said in a news release.</p>
<p>About 25 Fathom employees will join Think's Los Angeles office. Think New Idea is based in New York. Its shares closed up 15/16 to 4-1/16.</p>
